deleteTSV(25.10)                                              deleteTSV(25.10)

Name
       deleteTSV - Deletes the specified TSVs

Syntax
       deleteTSV

       {-all | -selected| -unassigned}

       Deletes  the  specified TSVs. If the TSV belongs to a feedthru, the en-
       tire feedthru will also be deleted.

Parameters
       -all   Deletes all the TSVs.

       -selected
              Deletes the selected TSVs.

       -unassigned
              Deletes the unassigned TSVs.

Examples
              * The following command deletes all the TSVs:

                deleteTSV -all

Related Information
              * addTSV

